    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>记录在 Windows 上配置基于输入法引擎 <strong>Rime</strong> 的小狼毫输入法 weasel 的过程</p><p>参考资料 &amp; 资源链接</p><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/rime/rime-double-pinyin">Github | rime&#x2F;rime-double-pinyin</a></li><li><a href="http://flypy.ysepan.com/">小鹤网盘</a></li><li><a href="https://github.com/rime/weasel/wiki/%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B">Github | rime&#x2F;weasel&#x2F;皮肤示例</a></li><li><a href="https://bennyyip.github.io/Rime-See-Me/">Rime-See-Me</a></li></ul></blockquote><h2 id="配置双拼方案"><a href="#配置双拼方案" class="headerlink" title="配置双拼方案"></a>配置双拼方案</h2><p>从 rime 官方的 <a href="https://github.com/rime/rime-double-pinyin">Github 仓库</a> 中可以找到 5 个 yaml 文件，对应 5 种双拼方案</p><figure class="highlight graphql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs graphql">double_pinyin.<span class="hljs-keyword">schema</span>.yaml <span class="hljs-comment"># 自然码双拼</span><br>double_pinyin_abc.<span class="hljs-keyword">schema</span>.yaml <span class="hljs-comment"># 智能 ABC 双拼</span><br>double_pinyin_flypy.<span class="hljs-keyword">schema</span>.yaml <span class="hljs-comment"># 小鹤双拼</span><br>double_pinyin_mspy.<span class="hljs-keyword">schema</span>.yaml <span class="hljs-comment"># MSPY 双拼</span><br>double_pinyin_pyjj.<span class="hljs-keyword">schema</span>.yaml <span class="hljs-comment"># 拼音加加双拼</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上输入方案均依赖于朙月拼音(luna-pinyin)，而 weasel 已经预装该方案，因此只需将相应双拼方案的 yaml 文件放入<strong>用户文件夹</strong>中，然后在 <code>default.custom.yaml</code> 中添加相应的补丁：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">patch:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">schema_list:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-attr">schema:</span> <span class="hljs-string">double_pinyin_flypy</span>&#125; <span class="hljs-comment"># 小鹤双拼</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着在 <code>double_pinyin_flypy.schema.yaml</code> 中的 <code>states: [ 漢字, 汉字 ]</code> 上方添加一行 <code>reset: 1</code> 以保证默认输入简体中文</p><p>最后<strong>重新部署</strong>即可</p><blockquote><p>注：重新部署时，在 <code>default.custom.yaml</code> 中的 patch 字段中所作的修改将作用到 <code>bin/default.yaml</code> 中；在 <code>weasel.custom.yaml</code> 中的 patch 字段中所作的修改将作用到 <code>bin/weasel.yaml</code> 中。每次<strong>重新部署</strong>时，<code>bin/default.yaml</code> 和 <code>bin/weasel.yaml</code> 将被格式化，如果在这两个文件中添加注释，将会被清楚，<code>default.custom.yaml</code> 和 <code>weasel.custom.yaml</code> 则不会（上述文件均以<strong>用户文件夹</strong>为起始位置）</p></blockquote><h2 id="配置小鹤音形"><a href="#配置小鹤音形" class="headerlink" title="配置小鹤音形"></a>配置小鹤音形</h2><p>在 <a href="http://flypy.ysepan.com/">小鹤网盘</a> 中的挂接音形码中找到 <code>小鹤音形”鼠须管“for macOS.zip</code> 文件进行下载（或从此<a href="http://ys-l.ysepan.com/116124357/319356963/VIg9jUm5G4J6J3686MM5c1/%E5%B0%8F%E9%B9%A4%E9%9F%B3%E5%BD%A2%E2%80%9C%E9%BC%A0%E9%A1%BB%E7%AE%A1%E2%80%9Dfor%20macOS.zip?lx=xz">下载链接</a> 下载）</p><p>下载完成后将 <code>rime/build</code> 中的所有文件复制到用户文件夹的 <code>build</code> 中，将 <code>rime</code> 中的 <code>flypy.schema.yaml</code> 和所有 <code>txt</code> 文件复制到 用户文件夹 中，并在 <code>default.custom.yaml</code> 中添加补丁启用小鹤音形：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">patch:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">schema_list:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-attr">schema:</span> <span class="hljs-string">flypy</span>&#125; <span class="hljs-comment"># 小鹤音形</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后重新部署即可</p><h2 id="皮肤、按键等个性化设置"><a href="#皮肤、按键等个性化设置" class="headerlink" title="皮肤、按键等个性化设置"></a>皮肤、按键等个性化设置</h2><blockquote><p>皮肤配置参考：<a href="https://github.com/rime/weasel/wiki/%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B">Github</a></p></blockquote><p>在 <code>default.custom.yaml</code> (<code>patch</code> 字段中) 添加如下内容 (以禁用方案选单快捷键 <code>Control+grave</code>，设置翻页快捷键 <code>[</code>和<code>]</code>，设置候选词数量)：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">patch:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">switcher:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">abbreviate_options:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">caption:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;[方案菜单]&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">fold_options:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">hotkeys:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-comment"># - &quot;Control+grave&quot;</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">F4</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">key_binder:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">bindings:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-attr">accept:</span> <span class="hljs-string">bracketleft</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">send:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Page_Up</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">when:</span> <span class="hljs-string">has_menu</span>&#125; <span class="hljs-comment"># 用方括号 [] 来换页</span><br>      <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-attr">accept:</span> <span class="hljs-string">bracketright</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">send:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Page_Down</span>, <span class="hljs-attr">when:</span> <span class="hljs-string">has_menu</span>&#125; <span class="hljs-comment"># 用方括号 [] 来换页</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;menu/page_size&quot;:</span> <span class="hljs-number">7</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 候选词数</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://github.com/rime/weasel/wiki/%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B">Rime 官方皮肤示例</a> 中展示了几种较为美观的皮肤颜色配置方案</p><h3 id="竖排-天圆地方"><a href="#竖排-天圆地方" class="headerlink" title="竖排 天圆地方"></a>竖排 天圆地方</h3><p><img src="/../img/image1.png" alt="竖排 天圆地方"></p>    <div class="fold">      <div class="fold-title fold-info collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse-05eef982" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-05eef982">        <div class="fold-arrow">▶</div>yaml 代码      </div>      <div class="fold-collapse collapse" id="collapse-05eef982">        <div class="fold-content">          <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-comment"># weasel.custom.yaml</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">patch:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">style/+:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">inline_preedit:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">label_font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">13</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">comment_font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">horizontal:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">layout:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">min_width:</span> <span class="hljs-number">160</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">margin_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">12</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">margin_y:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">candidate_spacing:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_spacing:</span> <span class="hljs-number">6</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_padding:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_padding_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">12</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">shadow_radius:</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">corner_radius:</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">shadow_offset_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">shadow_offset_y:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>        </div>      </div>    </div><h3 id="横排-天圆地方"><a href="#横排-天圆地方" class="headerlink" title="横排 天圆地方"></a>横排 天圆地方</h3><p><img src="/../img/image2.png" alt="横排 天圆地方"></p>    <div class="fold">      <div class="fold-title fold-info collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse-90469042" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-90469042">        <div class="fold-arrow">▶</div>yaml 代码      </div>      <div class="fold-collapse collapse" id="collapse-90469042">        <div class="fold-content">          <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-comment"># weasel.custom.yaml</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">patch:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">style/+:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">label_format:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;%s&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">inline_preedit:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">label_font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">comment_font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">14</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">horizontal:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">layout:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">max_width:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1200</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">min_width:</span> <span class="hljs-number">10</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">margin_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">margin_y:</span> <span class="hljs-number">6</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_spacing:</span> <span class="hljs-number">6</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_padding_y:</span> <span class="hljs-number">6</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">hilite_padding_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">shadow_radius:</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">corner_radius:</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">round_corner:</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">shadow_offset_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">shadow_offset_y:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>        </div>      </div>    </div><h3 id="Windows11-风格"><a href="#Windows11-风格" class="headerlink" title="Windows11 风格"></a>Windows11 风格</h3><p><img src="/../img/image3.png" alt="Windows11 风格"></p>    <div class="fold">      <div class="fold-title fold-info collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse-738764b7" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-738764b7">        <div class="fold-arrow">▶</div>yaml 代码      </div>      <div class="fold-collapse collapse" id="collapse-738764b7">        <div class="fold-content">          <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-comment"># weasel.custom.yaml</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">patch:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-string">style/+:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">label_format:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;%s&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">inline_preedit:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">label_font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">comment_font_point:</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">horizontal:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">color_scheme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">win11light</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">color_scheme_dark:</span> <span class="hljs-string">win11dark</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">layout:</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">min_width:</span> <span class="hljs-number">10</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">margin_x:</span> <span class="hljs-number">16</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">margin_y:</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">border:</s